Package curam.util.ctm.bom.businessobjectinformation

Contains the interfaces and implemetation classes for business object information and home page parameter used in CTM infrastructure

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BusinessObjectActionData
    Interface that groups BusinessObjectIdentifier and its related information which is primarily used to simplify passing related information to various BOM API methods.
    BusinessObjectInformation
    Defines a business object information object, used by business object modules to specify the details of the business object instance of a particular type.
    BusinessObjectInformationFactory
    Provides factory methods to create a BusinessObjectInformation and HomePageParameter.
    HomePageParameter
    Defines home page parameter, used by business object modules to specify the page parameter(s) associated with the home page of the business object.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BusinessObjectInformationFactoryImpl
    Standard implementation of BusinessObjectInformationFactory.
    BusinessObjectInformationImpl
    Standard implementation of BusinessObjectInformation.
    HomePageParameterImpl
    Standard implementation of HomePageParameter.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DeletionMode
    Enumeration that is modeled to identify the deletion modes which are applicable to a business object type.
